data.description: Imagine stepping into a home that feels both brand new and warmly inviting. This stunning residence boasts a modern open floor plan, accentuated by pristine white cabinets that give the kitchen and living areas a bright and airy feel. The heart of the home is the chef’s delight kitchen, complete with a stainless Steel appliances, puck lighting,  and ample storage space within the sleek cabinetry.    As you ascend the stairs, you’ll find the private sanctuary of the bedrooms. Each room is a peaceful retreat, very airy and bright, designed with comfort and tranquility in mind, offering a perfect end to your day. You will love the spacious master suite, with a bath featuring  a garden tub and separate shower, as well as large closet.    Located on the cul-de-sac, very close to all amenities of life.    This home merges functionality with elegance, providing a perfect backdrop for both relaxation and entertainment. With its thoughtful layout and contemporary design, it’s a place where memories are waiting to be made.
